name: Retribution, World #24
description:
| Retribution. |
|There are those among you who have already been let down. "Tell me do you really think you go to hell for having loved?" Tell me, would it suffice for you to push me up the wall, pull a gun up to my head, and just watch my brain pop? Well, you know you wouldn't even look at it, more than being the final scene for me it's a scar on your soul. Nobody ever got punished for loving they said, it's the only true thing to do they said."-The boy wrote in the journal. 
-Look, the sun is up but the night hasn't gone. 
-And it's not going to for the time being. 
Wake up slowly, the stars shining may scare you.
